# ── OS / editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak
*.tmp

# ── IDEs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
*.iml
.vscode/

# ── Android / Gradle — build outputs and local config ─────────────────────────
# Ignore generated build dirs anywhere in the tree
**/build/
# Ignore Gradle caches (downloaded dependencies, daemon state)
**/.gradle/
# local.properties contains the machine-specific Android SDK path — never commit
local.properties
# C++ native build cache
**/.cxx/
# App release signing artifacts
*.keystore
*.jks
!debug.keystore

# ── What NOT to ignore (Gradle project skeleton) ──────────────────────────────
# These files define the project and MUST be committed:
#   gradlew, gradlew.bat, gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar,
#   gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.properties, gradle/libs.versions.toml,
#   gradle/gradle-daemon-jvm.properties, build.gradle.kts,
#   settings.gradle.kts, gradle.properties, app/build.gradle.kts,
#   app/proguard-rules.pro
# None of the above match the patterns above, so they are tracked by default.

# ── Build artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.apk
*.aab
*.dex
*.class

# ── Rust (linux/campc-rust) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
*/target/